metadata.name: BLOCKED BLOBS #1 by Kindah Khalidy
metadata.description:
BLOCKED BLOBS #1 by Kindah Khalidy

The “Blocked Blobs” Series is Kindah Khalidy’s NFT debut. This series tells a narrative with a small cast of Kindah’s original characters filling the piece. It’s as if these groups of shapes are moving to their own personality.
All artwork in this series is original artwork, ideas, and property of Kindah Khalidy. 2022.
